    "description": "特里斯坦在一个神秘的世界中醒来后，遭到了以焦虑和恐惧为生的阴影的追杀。面对并克服他内心深处的恐惧，寻找逃离这场恐怖生存噩梦的方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/2eeee9353b20385c90b8aabb365672ae.poster.avif?t=1738230460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/2eeee9353b20385c90b8aabb365672ae.webm?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/2eeee9353b20385c90b8aabb365672ae.mp4?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索充斥着噩梦般恐惧表现的腐朽记忆。<br></li><li>在快节奏的战斗中使用各种武器、道具和能力（包括你的猫咪 Greg）进行反击。<br></li><li>在每个区域的终点正面挑战收割者之前，先避开在关卡中潜行的收割者。<br></li><li>选择最适合您玩法的游戏模式： 专注于故事情节，挑战更宽松的关卡，或者挑战令人抓狂的难度和额外的 BOSS 战。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/c3155dec02bf93e538bc878321d5d632.poster.avif?t=1738230460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/c3155dec02bf93e538bc878321d5d632.webm?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/c3155dec02bf93e538bc878321d5d632.mp4?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>体验一个引人入胜的故事，在充满创意的恐怖环境中学习如何应对焦虑、期望和悲伤。<br></li><li>通过寻找新装备、解锁各种战斗技能以及混合搭配灵魂来定制自己的装备，从而变得更加强大。<br></li><li>在森林中枢区域休息一下，这里有角色、任务、商店和技能树升级通道。<br></li><li>寻找并收集纪念品和成就，加深对诺克夏-索姆尼亚世界的了解。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现在就加入《诺克萨姆尼亚》预购清单！</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/ca46fc0f1bfd1b98ebd1ba1b3f2e13a1.poster.avif?t=1738230460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/ca46fc0f1bfd1b98ebd1ba1b3f2e13a1.webm?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278940/extras/ca46fc0f1bfd1b98ebd1ba1b3f2e13a1.mp4?t=1738230460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
